---
title: Homestyle Pumpkin & Leek Risotto with Basil Pesto & Parmesan Cheese
description: This roasted pumpkin and leek risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you to kick your feet up and enjoy quality time with the ones who matter. Basil pesto stirred through at the end adds a pop of bright flavour, elevating this dish to a whole new level of yum.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65d6ba68bb774993318afdc3-7e2f25fc.jpeg
